Shadow Wing/Fidgit

Fidgit: She was blown into the air from the blast at the Arc and was slammed 
into a tree.  She fell to the ground.  She fur sindged and her body heavily 
damaged. She tried to get up but fell back to the ground unconsious.


Shadow Wing:

She saw the blast as it came down and took to flight a split second before 
it hit.  She wasn't out of range of the blast and was sent screaming into 
the air bast the lower clouds and high up into the stratosphere.  She 
regained control and started to head back to the Arc.  She saw that part of 
it was destroyed.
"What the heck could obliterate part of the Arc like that?"
She looked around and flew up higher in time to see one bot carry off 
another bot.
"Hmm, I wonder."
She decided that the bots at the Arc would need help and flew down to 
assist.
